# 🧠 OS Concept 1: Observability & Monitoring Basics

## 1️⃣ Simple Idea

Large systems must constantly monitor:

✔ performance
✔ failures
✔ traffic
✔ errors

This is called:

👉 observability

---

## Main Components

---

## 🔹 Metrics

Numerical values:

```text id="3k7xpr"
CPU usage
Memory usage
Request count
```

---

## 🔹 Logs

Detailed event records.

---

## 🔹 Traces

Track request flow across services.

---

## 🧠 Real-World Analogy

Hospital monitoring patient health continuously.

---

## Why Important?

Without monitoring:

❌ failures hard to detect
❌ debugging difficult

---

## 🎯 Placement Question

**Q: Why observability important?**

👉 Because distributed systems are complex and need continuous monitoring for reliability.

---

## 🧠 Memory Trick

```text id="8v2mqt"
Observe system health continuously
```

