# ⚙️ COA Concept 4: Memory Compression Techniques

🔥 Practical system optimization topic.

---

## 1️⃣ Problem

Memory capacity limited.

---

## Solution

Compress memory contents.

Store more data in same RAM space.

---

## Benefits

✔ improved memory utilization
✔ fewer disk swaps
✔ better performance

---

## Tradeoff

Compression/decompression adds CPU overhead.

---

## 🧠 Real-World Analogy

Vacuum bags storing more clothes in same space.

---

## 🔗 Connection

Helps reduce:

* paging
* memory bottlenecks

---

## 🎯 Placement Question

**Q: Why memory compression useful?**

👉 It increases effective memory capacity and reduces swapping.

---

## 🧠 Memory Trick

```text id="2t8qvn"
Compress memory → fit more data
```

